%section.tagline
  %p
    = t "Make ideas into objects", "Trasforma le tue idee in oggetti"

%section.welcome
  - if en?
    :textile
      3DMaking is a lab specialized in 3D print. Rapid prototyping, customizable objects, "3D printers manufacturing":/printer_3dm1, tech assistance hardware and software are some of our services.
    %p
      If you still don't have an idea of what to 3d print, you can search in
      %a{href: "http://thingiverse.com"} thingiverse
      and select an already made 3d model.
  - else
    :textile
